text: Vanishing Waves (originally titled Aurora) is a 2012 Lithuanian French Belgian science fiction movie directed by Kristina Buožytė and starring Marius Jampolskis, Jurga Jutaitė, Rudolfas Jansonas, Vytautas Kaniušonis, Martina Jablonskyte, Darius Meškauskas. == Other websites == * Category:2012 science fiction movies Category:Lithuanian movies Category:French science fiction movies Category:Belgian science fiction movies
title: Vanishing Waves
